java.lang.Object

public class OverlayIcon
extends Overlay

This Overlay class displays a finite number of icons, with the image provided by the user

Author:
Se-Gil Feldsott and Justin Goldsmith StatInt stat = new StatInt(5); GreenfootImage image = new GreenfootImage("..."); OverlayIcon overlay = new OverlayIcon(stat, image, "Lives: ");
